<% title_style = 'font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900;' %>
<% value_style = 'margin-bottom: 1rem;overflow-wrap: break-word;' %>
<p>We detected a new transaction that adds credit to your GuessGoals wallet. Details are attached below for your reference.</p>

<div style="<%= title_style %>">Amount</div>
<div style="<%= value_style %>"><%= @amount %> BTC</div>

<div style="<%= title_style %>">Transaction Id</div>
<div style="<%= value_style %>"><%= @txid %></div>

<div style="<%= title_style %>">Received on Address</div>
<div style="<%= value_style %>"><%= @address %></div>

<div style="<%= title_style %>">Received at</div>
<div style="<%= value_style %>"><%= @performed_at %></div>

<p>
We will let you know when this transaction is confirmed. In the meantime, you can go ahead and use this credit towards betting on matches available on GuessGoals website.
Just keep in mind that we require one block confirmation of this transaction before the match you play on starts.
</p>
Enjoy Betting, <br>
